column5: Many Happy Returns my friend...  Three score and ten eh?
HAPPY BIRTHDAY my friend  hope you have a great day
Happy birthday Cliff? Hope u got my card and that u r feeling better The smoker works awesome Slater
~~~~Happy Birthday bud, congrats on making it so far.
All the best, Cliff. How's the leg?
Happy Birthday Cliff, hope you have the best day
I still have to meet this guy for a coffee, Happy Birthday Cliff! PS I'm still using the Lowrance I bought off you years ago.
Best of health on your day and all year long.
Happy B-day Cliff. I hope Sue spoils you.
Happy Birthday Big Cliff hope you have a Great Day. Tight Lines SBK
Happy BDAY Big man.
I wish you the best. How's that knee? Hope you can do a jig on your B Day.
Happy Big one Cliff!
Happy Birthday Cliff!
Happy birthday sir,hope you have a great one !!!!!
Happy birthday my friend. A celebration is long overdue.
Here's to many more!  Happy birthday!
One of these years I am going to meet you in person, I hope.  In the meantime, all the best!Doug
Dang guys (and gal) thank you all so much! I never in my wildest dreams thought I get to see 70 never mind still be able to put in a 14 hour work day (on my birthday no less LOL).
You have a kind heart which is going to see many more birthdays in the years to come.  Enjoy
You have a kind heart which is going to see many more birthdays in the years to come.  Enjoy Could never have said it any better for my friend
Happy birthday big guy!  Although I might be a day late.  Party at Cliff's tonight!!  Woo Hoo!

Happy birthday big guy!  Although I might be a day late.  Party at Cliff's tonight!!  Woo Hoo! Sorry, Sue greated me at the door wearing nothing but a big red bow.  Door is locked it's now a party for two
Happy belated b-day!
Cliff, take this from a man with a beard that is snow camo..............pour yourself a stiff one.  Doug
